We begin by defining the `UndergraduateStudent` class in a header file, say `UndergraduateStudent.h`. This class will encapsulate the essential attributes of a university undergraduate student: full name, unique student ID, and GPA. The class will also include methods for setting and getting these values, along with a method to display the student's profile.

